These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, coffee, lemonade, tea
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: december, november, april, february, august
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, vegafina, oliveros, alhambra, pall-mall
There 5 different types of food: raspberry, spinach, apple, potato, apricot
 1. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person eating apple##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is the person drinking coffee##1
 5. the person eating raspberry is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person eating potato##1
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person eating apple##1
11. the person drinking tea is between the vegafina-smoker and the person who's birthday is in august##2
12. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
13. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Beverage      | 7up        | almond-milk | tea     | coffee   | lemonade |
| Birthday   | april     | november      | february | august   | december    |
| Cigar   | alhambra  | vegafina     | ritmeester | oliveros | pall-mall  |
| Food           | spinach | apple      | apricot     | potato   | raspberry     |

