.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, game, baccarat, tiparillo, ritmeester
The people have 5 different jobs:  accountant, architect, firefighter, freelancer, electrician
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: june, august, september, january, april
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike, roller, scooter, skateboard
 1. the person driving the skateboard is in the middle##1
 2. the electrician is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
 3. the game-smoker is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 4. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person who's birthday is in june and the electrician##2
 6. the person driving the scooter is the game-smoker##1
 7. the accountant is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in september is the freelancer##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the game-smoker##1
10. the firefighter is on the right of the architect##1
11. the person who's birthday is in september is the baccarat-smoker##1
12. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Cigar         | tiparillo | alhambra | ritmeester    | game  | baccarat    |
| Job   | electrician    | architect       | firefighter      | accountant | freelancer        |
| Birthday   | april   | august     | june    | january  | september     |
| Transport     | roller    | quad-bike | skateboard | scooter | helicopter |

