.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: collecting, filmmaking, puzzles, rock-climbing, singing
5 different pets are kept: goat, lizard, hamster, bird, snake
House: art-deco, cape-cod, craftsman, victorian, ranch-style
There are 5 different nationalities: japanese, brazilian, french, dutch, argentine
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is the cape-cod house##1
 2. the dutch is in the middle##1
 3. the victorian house is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the goat is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the brazilian##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the art-deco house##1
 7. the ranch-style house is on the left of the french##1
 8. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 9. the craftsman house is on the far left##1
10. the japanese is the owner of the bird##1
11. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the argentine##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
13. the argentine is between the owner of the snake and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | collecting | singing     | puzzles   | filmmaking   | rock-climbing |
| Pet   | snake  | lizard | goat | bird | hamster        |
| House   | craftsman      | cape-cod      | victorian       | ranch-style       | art-deco       |
| Nationality         | brazilian | argentine  | dutch    | japanese    | french        |

