.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
House: gothic-revival, ranch-style, townhouse, art-deco, tower
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, puzzles, singing, skydiving, woodworking
The people use 5 different means of transport: trike, quad-bike, airplane, helicopter, motorbike
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, tiparillo, bluemaster, davidoff, montecristo
 1. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 3. the ranch-style house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 4. the montecristo-smoker is between the person driving the helicopter and the art-deco house##2
 5. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 6. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 9. the person driving the motorbike is in the middle##1
10. the person driving the helicopter is the oliveros-smoker##1
11. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
12. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
13. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| House          | tower  | townhouse     | art-deco   | ranch-style     | gothic-revival |
| Hobby         | woodworking | cooking    | singing  | skydiving | puzzles   |
| Transport   | quad-bike        | trike    | motorbike     | airplane     | helicopter    |
| Cigar   | tiparillo    | bluemaster | davidoff | montecristo | oliveros   |

