.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: indie, funk, techno, folk, hip-hop
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, montecristo, swisher, aristoff, davidoff
The people have 5 different jobs:  dancer, lawyer, manager, social-worker, writer
5 different pets are kept: dog, pony, hamster, fish, horse
 1. the owner of the pony is on the right of the dancer##1
 2. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
 3. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 4. the fan of techno is between the owner of the pony and the pall-mall-smoker##2
 5. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 6. the fan of folk is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
 7. the fan of folk is on the left of the lawyer##1
 8. the writer is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 9. the fan of funk is on the far right##1
10. the fan of funk is on the right of the dancer##1
11. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
12. the social-worker is on the left of the dancer##1
13. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | hip-hop       | indie   | techno      | funk    |
| Cigar       | davidoff | aristoff        | pall-mall       | swisher       | montecristo |
| Job        | writer     | lawyer        | social-worker | dancer        | manager  |
| Pet      | fish | hamster | dog      | horse | pony  |

