The people prefer 5 different music-genres: funk, r&b, folk, pop, electronic
 1. the project-manager is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
 2. the fan of folk is on the right of the doctor##1
 3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the french##1
 5. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 6. the owner of the bird is between the accountant and the fan of r&b##2
 7. the fan of folk is the turkish##1
 8. the australian is on the far right##1
 9. the doctor is on the right of the french##1
10. the fan of pop is on the far right##1
11. the lawyer is between the accountant and the fan of r&b##2
12. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the polish##1
13. the accountant is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |     5      |
| Pet      | lizard  | bird      | goldfish   | hamster   | goat   |
| Job   | accountant    | lawyer   | doctor   | scientist | project-manager     |
