 7. the videographer is the person who's birthday is in march##1
 8. the person who likes light-blue is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
10. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person who likes apricot##1
11. the person who's birthday is in july is the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
