5 different games are played: bridge, billiard, backgammon, mah-jongg, poker
There are 5 different favourite colors: chestnut, orange, brown, turquise, light-blue
 1. the bartender is between the person playing mah-jongg and the chef##2
 2. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
 3. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
 4. the person who likes chestnut is in the middle##1
 5. the dancer is the person watching horror movies##1
 6. the person watching family movies is between the person playing backgammon and the manager##2
 7. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
 8. the person watching horror movies is the person who likes brown##1
 9. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the bartender##1
10. the person playing poker is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
11. the dancer is on the left of the bartender##1
12. the person playing bridge is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |    5    |
