 1. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 2. the bolivar-smoker is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 3. the person playing scrabble is the bluemaster-smoker##1
 4. the person playing go is the game-smoker##1
 5. the havana-smoker is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking juice is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
