 8. the person who growsazalea is in the middle##1
 9. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
10. the person who growsdahlia is between the bluemaster-smoker and the person drinking 7up##2
11. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
12. the person who growsdaffodil is the person playing mah-jongg##1

