.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-17::.
City: berlin, rome, boston, hannover, nizza
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: april, may, september, december, august
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, golf, handball, sailing
5 different games are played: whist, canasta, scrabble, monopoly, domino
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person playing canasta and the person who's sport is cricket##2
 2. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person traveling to rome is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 4. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 5. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 7. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
10. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1
11. the person playing scrabble is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's birthday is in september##2
12. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
13. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| City    | boston       | hannover    | nizza | rome  | berlin        |
| Birthday       | august | april | september  | december | may    |
| Sport       | golf        | handball   | cricket  | sailing   | basketball |
| Game   | monopoly       | scrabble      | domino      | whist | canasta  |

