 2. the fisherman is between the mexican and the entrepreneur##2
 3. the person traveling to nizza is the fisherman##1
 4. the australian is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 5. the thai is in the middle##1
 6. the person traveling to nizza is between the pilot and the owner of the snake##2
 7. the owner of the hedgehog is the person traveling to new-york##1
 8. the person traveling to paris is the owner of the pony##1
 9. the owner of the rat is on the left of the pilot##1
10. the bartender is on the right of the mexican##1
11. the entrepreneur is the italian##1
12. the egyptian is on the far left##1
13. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
