5 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, guinea-pig, lizard, mouse
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, ritmeester, chaman, havana, oliveros
 1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 2. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 3. the person playing canasta is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
 4. the chaman-smoker is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is between the person who growsamaryllis and the owner of the cat##2
 6. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left##1
 7. the person playing mah-jongg is between the tiparillo-smoker and the person playing canasta##2
 8. the person playing snooker is between the person playing bridge and the person playing ritmeesterd-games##2
 9. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person playing ritmeesterd-games##1
10. the person playing ritmeesterd-games is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1

