.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, hiking, reading, blend-climbing, skydiving
There are 5 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, sprite, fanta, water, hot-chocolate
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, chaman, cain, tiparillo, blend
There are 5 different favourite colors: lilac, green, fuchsia, yellow, turquise
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person who likes yellow and the blend-smoker##2
 3. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the bluemaster-smoker##1
 5. the bluemaster-smoker is between the person who likes turquise and the cain-smoker##2
 6. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 7. the person drinking fanta is the tiparillo-smoker##1
 8. the person who's hobby is blend-climbing is the chaman-smoker##1
 9. the person who likes lilac is the chaman-smoker##1
10. the person who's hobby is blend-climbing is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
12. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | reading    | skydiving  | hiking  | cooking      | blend-climbing |
| Beverage   | sprite    | hot-chocolate   | water | fanta | soy-milk   |
| Cigar   | cain | bluemaster    | blend    | tiparillo       | chaman         |
| Color   | yellow  | green | turquise    | fuchsia     | lilac      |

 